25 OMBUD'S OFFICE FUNDING
26 SECTION 2.3.(a) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Department
27 of Administration, State Human Resources Commission, the sum of one hundred eighty thousand
28 dollars ($180,000) in recurring funds for each year of the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium for two new
29 personnel positions to support establishment of the Ombud's Office created by this act.
30 SECTION 2.3.(b) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Department
31 of Administration, State Human Resources Commission, the sum of one hundred thousand
32 dollars ($100,000) in nonrecurring funds for each year of the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium to fund
33 enforcement, training, and educational efforts concerning G.S. 126-101, as enacted by this act,
34 and to combat workplace bullying in State government.
35 SECTION 2.3.(c) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Department
36 of Labor the sum of seventy-seven thousand dollars ($77,000) in recurring funds for each year
37 of the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium for one new personnel position to conduct investigations related
38 to the enforcement of G.S. 126-101, as enacted by this act.
39 SECTION 2.3.(d) This section becomes effective July 1, 2025.
