47 PART IV. LOCAL GOVERNMENT PROTECTIONS
48
49 NO BAN ON LOCAL MINIMUM WAGES
50 SECTION 3.1. Sections 5.9(a), 5.9(b), and 5.9(c) of S.L. 2023-134 are repealed.
